, \"from\": 300, \"to\": 318}, {\"ngram\": \"the rape\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"a 12-year-old English girl\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sorry, this video is not available any more.\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this video\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aged 19 at the time of the crime, Van de Velde served just 12 months of his four-year sentence and has since managed to rebuild his career in the sport, leading to his selection in the Netherlands' Olympic squad.\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9702808312160223, \"rank\": 0.030626958340124008, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 460}, {\"ngram\": \"the crime\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 487}, {\"ngram\": \"just 12 months\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"his four-year sentence\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"his selection\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout the tournament, though, Van de Velde - competing alongside fellow countryman Matthew Immers - was subjected to boos and jeers and Dutch Olympic bosses repeatedly stood by the 30-year-old amid an onslaught of criticism.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 796, \"end\": 801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9911965243668358, \"rank\": 0.00831730861657379, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde - competing alongside fellow countryman Matthew Immers\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"boos\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 781}, {\"ngram\": \"jeers\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"an onslaught\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"criticism\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde's participation in Paris was ultimately brought to an end by Brazil's pairing of Evandro Oliveira and Arthur Diego Mariano Lanci, who defeated their Dutch counterparts in straight sets at the round-of-16 stage.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999554348, \"rank\": 4.466362463480953e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 960, \"end\": 966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999970603605568, \"rank\": 2.798585551421361e-06, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 980, \"end\": 996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evandro_Oliveira\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evandro Oliveira\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evandro_Oliveira\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evandro_Oliveira\"}, {\"begin\": 1001, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_Arthur\", \"score\": 0.9872368338294848, \"rank\": 0.012928170559602239, \"text\": \"Arthur\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_Arthur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_Arthur\"}, {\"begin\": 1008, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego\", \"score\": 0.9494106980333751, \"rank\": 0.05328495039763082, \"text\": \"Diego\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego\"}, {\"begin\": 1014, \"end\": 1021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Mariano\", \"score\": 0.9723684007259401, \"rank\": 0.021133838879358418, \"text\": \"Mariano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Mariano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Mariano\"}, {\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9911965243668358, \"rank\": 0.00831730861657379, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde's participation\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"an end\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"straight sets\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"the round-of-16 stage\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The controversial athlete largely remained tight-lipped in the French capital, refusing to face questioning in the mixed zone after matches.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8446790729817536, \"rank\": 0.17108171711167047, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The controversial athlete\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed zone\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"matches\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Van de Velde has broken his silence upon his return to the Netherlands.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1320, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9702808312160223, \"rank\": 0.030626958340124008, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"his silence\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"his return\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked whether he had considered not competing in the Games, Van de Velde replied: 'I definitely thought about it, yes.'\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde says he could not accept the invasion into his private life, which involved his loves ones getting 'hurt'.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1467}, {\"ngram\": \"the invasion\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"his private life\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"his loves ones\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That's when I broke down,' Van de Velde added, referring to a British tabloid using a picture of his wife in a story.\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1639, \"end\": 1646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9941428426671722, \"rank\": 0.004793994853663476, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"a picture\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"a story\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I did something wrong, ten years ago.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have to accept that.\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But hurting people around me - whether it's Matthew, my wife, my child\\u2026 that just goes too far for me.\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"Matthew\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1811}, {\"ngram\": \"my wife\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"my child\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's definitely a moment where I thought, is this worth it?'\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1925, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Michel Everaert, the general manager of Nevobo (Netherlands Volleyball), meanwhile, insisted the storm surrounding Van de Velde had been 'dredged up' by British media.\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2080, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9941428426671722, \"rank\": 0.004793994853663476, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\